-- China Continues Ban on Establishing New Airlines, Business News Reports
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-10-20T22:49:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-20/china-continues-ban-on-establishing-new-airlines-business-news-reports.html
The Civil Aviation Administration of
China will continue to not accept applications for the
establishment of new airlines, China Business News reported,
citing an unidentified airline official.  The regulator stopped accepting applications in 2007,
saying at the time that the policy would last for three years,
the newspaper reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
 jliu42@bloomberg.net  